snippet.title: SMB Hack Walkthrough - Mushroom Heaven
snippet.description:
If you enjoyed watching this video please give us thumbs up, leave a comment below, share this video with others! Press the bell icon to get notified about new videos. It will greatly help us make more content like this.

A walkthrough for SMB1 hack is Mushroom Heaven.

Mario suddenly finds himself as an angel in a lovely sky kingdom.

This hack has multiple endings, and takes place in one giant continuous level. No flagpoles, no time limit, no dying.

This hack is designed for beginners, please give it a try no matter your skill level!

Hack made by sinksadventure.

Download: https://www.romhacking.net/hacks/6803/

Follow me on Twitter: https://twitter.com/amyrose2904

#smbhack #longplay​​​​​​​​ #roadto100ksubscribers​
